title: Dorling Kindersley Visual Dictionary of Science (DK Ebook)
description:
Dorling Kindersley Ultimate Visual Dictionary of Science
Dorling Kindersley | 1998 | ISBN 0789435128 | English | 456 pages | PDF | 92 MB

This reference work is a guide to the main scientific disciplines, from the workings of plants, animals and the human body, through the principles of physics and chemistry, to the fundamentals of the universe. Each section provides an overview of an area of science and its main terms. An introduction explains and defines, while the extensive labeling of images should help the reader to understand. Special sections spotlight the most influential scientists and the critical moments in the history of scientific development
